Glavunion, which last year became the first Czech company to issue
medium-term bonds in the domestic market, will use the proceeds of the
offering to finance its Kcs2.6bn investment programme.
The notes were placed with Czech banks and other financial institutions,
said an official at lead manager CSFB.
